name.jp: ラブリィフェアリーの翼

description.en: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.ar: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.br:
A língua de ferro soou à meia-noite.
Ao leito, amantes; já é hora das fadas.
description.cns: 午夜十二点的钟声已经敲响；恋人上床睡觉；这几乎是童话时代。
description.fi: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.fil: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.id: Dengan lidahnya yang manis dia berbisik kepada kedua belas kekasihnya ditempat tidur, waktunya berdongeng.
description.it: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.jp: 真夜中の鉄の舌は12を語った。ベッドに愛好家、ほぼ妖精の時間です。
description.kr: 한밤중의 철 혀가 열두 사람에게 말했습니다. 잠자리에 드는 연인; 거의 요정의 시간입니다.
description.nl: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.pl: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.ru: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.sp: La lengua de hierro de la medianoche ha dicho doce; amantes a la cama; es casi la hora de las hadas.
description.sw: The iron tongue of midnight hath told twelve; lovers to bed; 'tis almost fairy time.
description.th: ลิ้นเหล็กของเที่ยงคืนบอกสิบสอง; คนรักนอน; ใกล้ถึงเวลานางฟ้าแล้ว
description.tw: 午夜的鐵舌已在十二點敲鐘了； 戀人上床睡覺，這幾乎是童話時代。
description.vi: Lưỡi sắt của nửa đêm đã nói mười hai lần; người yêu lên giường; đó là khoảng thời gian thần thánh
